# Agent orchestration

## Entry points

| User intent | Command / skill |
|-------------|-----------------|
| Fix tests | `/fix-tests`, `uploadm8-eval-loop` |
| Full cycle | `/ascended-loop`, `uploadm8-agent-orchestrator` |
| Deep plan | `/ultrathink`, `uploadm8-ultrathink` |
| Eval-driven feature | `/ultracode`, `uploadm8-ultracode` |
| Parallel lanes | `/five-windows`, `uploadm8-worktrees` |
| Both repos | `/multi-repo-ship`, `uploadm8-multi-repo` |
| CI red | `uploadm8-ascended-ci` |
| Unsure workflow | `python scripts/agent/dynamic_workflow.py --json` |
| **Full stack / go live** | **`/trill`**, **`trill`** skill |

## Parallel pattern

One turn, multiple Task subagents:

```
explore + bugbot + ci-investigator (when CI failing)
```

## Hooks enforce

- sessionStart → read AGENTS.md
- afterFileEdit → suggest tests
- beforeShellExecution → block force-push main, .env staging
- subagentStop → chain eval_loop after review

## Headless

Long runs: Task with `run_in_background: true` + `subagent_type: shell`.

## Agent-built tooling

Register repeat scripts via `scripts/agent/register_tool.py` and `uploadm8-agent-tooling` skill.
